# BCCR CA trust chain — the app's DEFAULT anchor for verifying signatures.
#
# Replace this file with the verified national CA chain, ROOT FIRST:
#   1) CA RAÍZ NACIONAL - COSTA RICA   (must be the FIRST certificate — it is the anchor)
#   2) CA POLÍTICA ... (optional; intermediates also arrive embedded in the signature)
#
# Verify the fingerprint out-of-band before trusting it
# (see docs/smartcard-commands.md §4). Until a real certificate block is present
# here, the app has no built-in default and you must load one in Configuración.
#
# Lines outside -----BEGIN/END CERTIFICATE----- blocks (like these) are ignored.
